   ---------------type script
   type script is an improved version of java script
   it is a static typing  means we need to provide type
   js:let age=26
   ts:let age:number=25
  ts doesnot allow different type to saved
  let age=25
   age="hello"---dont work in ts but works in js
   let name:string="anu"
   console.log(name)
   let status:boolean=true


   error checking

   in js error checking after running
   in ts error checking is before running ie compile time

   extension
   .ts
more code safety 


npm install -g typescript--install
g for global to use in all project

tsc -v--verify installtion

tsc is execute for compile
after compling ts is converted to js
then run nomally as js
node typescript_sample.js to run the file


BDD

Behaviour driven development.It is not build int Pw.we use tools like cucumber
the code is written in english it is called gherkin
Format for Jegherkinrkin
Feature:Login-----describes the functionality
Scenario:succesful Login----------describes a testcase
Given:Pre condition
when:User enters valid creds------action performed
then: expected result
and:additional steps

Install cucumber
npm install @cucumber/cucumber

Changes in  Packages.js>>to support e 6 later version


run commands: npx cucumber-js --require step-definitions/**/*.js


Hooks in cucumber
BeforeAll runs only once before all Scenarios
eg:Broswer Launch

2.AfterAll execute only once after all Scenarios are completed

3.Before:exceutes before each Scenario
eg:Pages set up 
4:After:Excutes after each Scenarios

5.BeforeStep:exceutes before every steps in a Scenario
eg:Screenshot
6:AfterStep:exceutes after  every steps in a Scenario
